title: '[[id:abb4ed18-7bcb-4865-93a1-2591ceb0c8ea][enlightenment]] as being at [[id:6e44fba3-c51d-430c-81ac-bd91e8db773b][peace]] with time and karma'
pid: de853810-a055-4b38-8b5e-0f0c65342383
body: |2-
  "Chop wood, carry water": What changes internally?

  A guess: After enlightenment, one takes very similar actions,
  but now believing in oneself|society,
  recognizing (having faith in?) the karmic perfection of slowly grinding gears.
